CN">永远都不会厌倦 我无法离开</span></p><p begin="00:42.332" end="00:45.512" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="00:42.332" end="00:42.441">If</span> <span begin="00:42.441" end="00:42.663">you</span> <span begin="00:42.663" end="00:42.895">want,</span> <span begin="00:42.895" end="00:43.098">well,</span> <span begin="00:43.098" end="00:43.208">I</span> <span begin="00:43.244" end="00:43.395">got</span> <span begin="00:43.395" end="00:43.588">it,</span> <span begin="00:43.588" end="00:43.746">I</span> <span begin="00:43.778" end="00:43.948">got</span> <span begin="00:43.948" end="00:44.097">it</span> <span begin="00:44.097" end="00:44.468">eve</span><span begin="00:44.513" end="00:44.877">ry</span><span begin="00:44.877" end="00:45.512">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要你想要 好吧 我就满足你 我每天都能满足你</span></p><p begin="00:45.596" end="00:48.315" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="00:45.596" end="00:45.801">You</span> <span begin="00:45.801" end="00:45.945">can</span> <span begin="00:45.945" end="00:46.135">get</span> <span begin="00:46.135" end="00:46.529">what</span><span begin="00:46.529" end="00:46.663">e</span><span begin="00:46.663" end="00:46.889">ver</span> <span begin="00:46.889" end="00:47.054">you</span> <span begin="00:47.054" end="00:47.383">need</span> <span begin="00:47.404" end="00:47.764">from</span> <span begin="00:47.764" end="00:48.315">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你可以从我这里得到你需要的一切</span></p><p begin="00:48.503" end="00:50.644" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="00:48.503" end="00:48.694">Stay</span> <span begin="00:48.694" end="00:48.837">by</span> <span begin="00:48.837" end="00:49.021">your</span> <span begin="00:49.021" end="00:49.406">side,</span> <span begin="00:49.406" end="00:49.590">I'll</span> <span begin="00:49.590" end="00:49.954">never</span> <span begin="00:49.954" end="00:50.307">leave</span> <span begin="00:50.307" end="00:50.644">ya</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" 